    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, renowned for its 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is paired with a longitudinal 6-speed manual transmission, delivering torque through a variable M differential lock for optimal mechanical grip. The chassis remains tight, equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and multi-link rear suspension geometry that ensures precise kinemantics during high-lateral G maneuvers. Recent preventative maintenance includes a rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacement, ensuring the internal tolerances and VANOS system operate within factory specifications. Finished with staggered forged wheels and cross-drilled rotors, this M3 offers a visceral, analog driving experience with proven mechanical longevity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
